Package org.hrw.datamodels

Interface Datastructure

All Known Implementing Classes:
HashRecord, ServerRecord
public interface Datastructure
Marker interface for data objects that can be persisted in the database.

Implementations must provide their attribute (column) names as a comma-separated string, which is used by the database layer to dynamically create SQL INSERT statements.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type
    Method
    Description
    String
    getAttributeNames()
    Returns the comma-separated list of attribute names corresponding to the database columns of this data structure.
